c/html/rfc6749\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">rfc6749</a>\n<a href=\"https://auth0.com/intro-to-iam/what-is-oauth-2/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">What is OAuth 2.0? - auth0</a>\n<a href=\"https://www.digitalocean.com/community/tutorials/an-introduction-to-oauth-2\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">An Introduction to OAuth 2 - DigitalOcean</a></p>","frontmatter":{"title":"OAuth 2.0","date":"January 12, 2022","category":"Web"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/web/oauth2/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/javascript/async-and-await/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"자바스크립트 async & await"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/web/authentication-vs-authorization/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"인증(Authentication)과 인가(Authorization)"}}}},"staticQueryHashes":[]}